Author: OodietcokeheadoO
Text: I was in your shoes not too long ago. I went from 183 to 109 in about a year and a half. 109 is the lowest I've e we been. I told a friend just today I had been eating 5-700 Cal's and she just told me I was doing a good job and she needs to do it, too. I still get complimented and congratulated for my weight loss by everyone irl. *Shrug* don't wait around for anyone to notice. You'll starve to death first lol
